# commands.in.txt

# Device is already restored with the correct seed
# Authenticate
/password my-password-1

# Get the `xpub` testnet segwit
/xpub Testnet m/84'/1'/0'

# Get address at derivation path
/address Testnet m/84'/1'/0'/0/3

# Sign the PSBT
/psbt Testnet 

# Logout. Note that "Logout" also takes place when the devices is rebooted.
/password-clear
